To build the kernel module:
$ make -C /lib/modules/$(uname -r)/build M=$PWD modules

To remove the kernel Module:

$ sudo rmmod peripheral_driver_main.ko

To load the kernel module:

$ sudo insmod peripheral_driver_main.ko

To see if module is available:
$ lsmod | more

To check the build driver:

cat /pro

To write to driver:
echo hi > /dev/mynull 

To Read from driver:
cat /dev/mynull

To see if device class is part of driver list:
cat /proc/devices

